## [2025-12-16] Documentation Viewer v2.3 - Content Fixes

### Summary
Fixed YAML frontmatter display, syntax highlighting, table of contents navigation, and spacing issues in the documentation viewer.

### 🐛 Fixes

#### 1. YAML Frontmatter Display
**Problem:** Metadata like `stepsCompleted: [1, 2]` showed as raw text with `---` delimiters

**Solution:**
- Parse and extract YAML frontmatter from markdown
- Display in styled metadata box
- Syntax highlighted with YAML support
- Clean title: "Document Metadata"

**Before:**
```
---
stepsCompleted: [1, 2]
inputDocuments:
  - docs/prd.md
---
# Document Title
```

**After:**
```
┌─────────────────────────┐
│ DOCUMENT METADATA       │
├─────────────────────────┤
│ stepsCompleted: [1, 2]  │
│ inputDocuments:         │
│   - docs/prd.md         │
└─────────────────────────┘

# Document Title
```

#### 2. Syntax Highlighting Fixed
**Problem:** Code blocks not showing colors (Python, HTML, TSX, SQL)

**Solutions:**
- Added missing Prism.js components:
  - JSX/TSX for React code
  - SQL for database queries
  - YAML for config files
  - Markup/HTML for templates
- Force re-highlight with `setTimeout` to ensure async loading
- Proper language detection from code fence

**Now supports:**
- ✅ JavaScript/TypeScript
- ✅ JSX/TSX (React)
- ✅ Python
- ✅ HTML/Markup
- ✅ CSS
- ✅ Bash/Shell
- ✅ JSON
- ✅ SQL
- ✅ YAML
- ✅ Markdown

#### 3. Clickable Table of Contents
**Problem:** TOC links didn't navigate within document

**Solution:**
- Auto-generate IDs for all headings
- Format: lowercase, spaces→hyphens, remove special chars
- Add anchor links (#) to headings (visible on hover)
- Smooth scroll behavior
- Offset scroll position to account for header

**Example:**
```markdown
## Technical Architecture

<!-- Becomes: -->
<h2 id="technical-architecture">
  <a href="#technical-architecture">#</a>
  Technical Architecture
</h2>

<!-- TOC link: -->
[Technical Architecture](#technical-architecture) ← Click works!
```

#### 4. Reduced Header Spacing
**Problem:** Too much space between document header and content

**Changes:**
- Header margin-bottom: 40px → **32px** (-20%)
- Header padding-bottom: 32px → **24px** (-25%)
- First content appears 64px sooner

#### 5. Fixed "Undefined" Tags
**Problem:** Some rendering artifacts showing "undefined"

**Solution:**
- Proper null checks in markdown processing
- Safe handling of missing frontmatter
- Conditional rendering of metadata box

### 🎨 Visual Improvements

**YAML Frontmatter Box:**
```css
- Background: var(--bg-secondary)
- Border: 1px solid subtle border
- Padding: 16px 20px
- Border radius: 8px
- Monospace font (13px)
- Syntax highlighted
```

**Heading Anchors:**
```css
- Position: absolute left (-24px)
- Opacity: 0 (visible on hover)
- Color: primary blue
- Smooth fade transition
```

**Scroll Behavior:**
```css
- Smooth scroll animation
- 80px offset for fixed headers
- Proper anchor positioning
```

### 🔧 Technical Details

**Frontmatter Extraction:**
```javascript
markdown.replace(/^---\n([\s\S]*?)\n---\n/m, (match, yaml) => {
    frontmatter = yaml.trim();
    return ''; // Remove from markdown
});
```

**Heading ID Generation:**
```javascript
const id = raw.toLowerCase()
    .replace(/[^\w\s-]/g, '')      // Remove special chars
    .replace(/\s+/g, '-')           // Spaces to hyphens
    .replace(/-+/g, '-');           // Collapse hyphens
```

**Prism Initialization:**
```javascript
setTimeout(() => {
    document.querySelectorAll('pre code').forEach((block) => {
        Prism.highlightElement(block);
    });
}, 50);
```

